This is called when a Game is started (new) or loaded. Of course - as this Instance only runs if Serenity is installed. It won't run if Serenity is not installed. Enable ROCs for all new games. But can Add logic here to change the rules.

This is called when a Game is loaded (existing). If the Game.ROCSeed is > -1 it has a seed - so Set ROCs ON for this Game. If the Game.ROCSeed is -1 it's an old existing game (pre DLC) - so Set ROCs OFF for this Game.
